channel.title: Compile error
channel.description:
I have a Mac computer, I go into Terminal, type "cd (Source)" and hit enter then I go into my Compile.bat and copy/paste this into terminal.
@echo off title Compiler "C:/Program Files/Java\jdk1.6.0_13/bin/javac.exe" -d ./bin ./src/*.java pause
and an error popped up. "-bash: C:/Program Files/Java\jdk1.6.0_13/bin/javac.exe: No such file or directory"
Help? :c
